# Step 5: Update Record

### API Endpoint

```http
PUT https://{{domain}}.dam.aprimo.com/api/core/record/{{recordId}}
```

### Purpose

Update the field:

```text
calculated_expiration_date
```

with the newly calculated earliest expiration date.

### Example Payload

```json
{
  "fields": {
    "addOrUpdate": [
      {
        "id": "{{calculatedExpirationDateFieldId}}",
        "localizedValues": [
          {
            "value": "2028-08-20"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

### Success Outcome

